<taxonomicName id="A96AD923C69AFDABE28A6877B1E6E05F" LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:30450" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Leptothorax" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leptothorax vicinus Mayr" lsidName-HNS="Leptothorax vicinus Mayr" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="28" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicinus">L. vicinus</taxonomicName>
, ma e agevole distinguerlo dalla scultura del torace.
</paragraph>
